text:
Prawn noodles soup is really yummy. We had previous bought take away but today we decided to have it here.

Noodles nicely mixed and spice levels can be adjusted. Prawns were fresh. The soup was the winner!!!! Delicious.

noodles and vegs were a little overdone but still within acceptable range - nevertheless a tasty bowl with a hefty amount of fresh ingredients - will patronise again. nice touch with the pig skin, appreciate such details and effort
